title: Gift Card v2.2 Codecanyon Woocommerce Wordpress Plugin
description:
Image : http://i.imgur.com/Clty0hb.jpg

Demo : http://codecanyon.net/item/woocommerce-gift-card/6234900

Woocommerce Gift Card plugin allows you to sell redeemable gift cards on your Woocommerce store. The gift cards are coupon codes which are generated automatically and can be applied to carts or products at checkout. It gets more interesting as you can send gift cards to other people.
